---

## How to Apply Fixes

### Backend (Python)
```bash
cd backend
rm -rf venv/
python3.11 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Frontend (Node.js)
```bash
cd frontend
nvm install 20.10.0
nvm use 20.10.0
rm -rf node_modules package-lock.json
npm install
npm run build
```

### Validation
```bash
cd backend && python -c "import fastapi, sqlalchemy, pinecone; print('✓ All Python imports OK')"
cd frontend && npm list --depth=0
```

